                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Sandalwood Elephant Carving</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Sandalwood carving of a friendly elephant commonly known amongst the community, in the Kruger National Park.</p>
                            <p class="card-text">Price: R649.99</p>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary">Add to Cart</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card mb-3">
