                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Hand Woven Tapestry</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Made with 100% rope - This dainty and light Cotton wall hanging is made with natural high quality four 
                                strands of rope and wooden dowel. Simple yet meticulously handcrafted, sturdy and durable. </p>
                            <p class="card-text">Price: R2499.99</p>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary">Add to Cart</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
